<div style='position:absolute;left:8px;top:3px;font-style:normal;font-weight:bold;font-size:36px;font-family:arial,"times new roman",times,serif;color:#4E256F;'>Forward&#45;looking statements</div>
<div style='position:absolute;left:917px;top:658px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;font-size:15px;font-family:arial,"times new roman",times,serif;color:#4D4D4D;'>1</div>
<div style='position:absolute;left:43px;top:112px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;font-size:19px;font-family:arial,"times new roman",times,serif;color:#000000;'>This</div>
<div style='position:absolute;left:89px;top:112px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;font-size:19px;font-family:arial,"times new roman",times,serif;color:#000000;'>presentation</div>
<div style='position:absolute;left:202px;top:112px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;font-size:19px;font-family:arial,"times new roman",times,serif;color:#000000;'>contains</div>
<div style='position:absolute;left:283px;top:112px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;font-size:19px;font-family:arial,"times new roman",times,serif;color:#000000;'>a</div>
<div style='position:absolute;left:303px;top:112px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;font-size:19px;font-family:arial,"times new roman",times,serif;color:#000000;'>number</div>
<div style='position:absolute;left:377px;top:112px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;font-size:19px;font-family:arial,"times new roman",times,serif;color:#000000;'>of</div>
<div style='position:absolute;left:403px;top:112px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;font-size:19px;font-family:arial,"times new roman",times,serif;color:#000000;'>forward&#45;looking</div>
<div style='position:absolute;left:541px;top:112px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;font-size:19px;font-family:arial,"times new roman",times,serif;color:#000000;'>statements.</div>

full&#45;year 2010, full&#45;year 2011 and the nine months to </div> <div style='position:absolute;left:200px;top:635px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;font-size:11px;font-family:arial,"times new roman",times,serif;color:#000000;'>September 30,

fees, U.K. stamp taxes and the impact of the Cadbury inventory revaluation.</div>
<div style='position:absolute;left:177px;top:641px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;font-size:7px;font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;'>Acquisition&#45;related financing fees include hedging and foreign currency impacts associated with
the Cadbury acquisition and other fees associated with the Cadbury Bridge Facility.</div>
<div style='position:absolute;left:177px;top:651px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;font-size:7px;font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;'>Restructuring Program costs represent non&#45;recurring restructuring and related implementation costs
reflecting primarily severance, asset disposals and other manufacturing related non&#45;</div>
<div style='position:absolute;left:177px;top:661px;font-style:normal;font-weight:normal;font-size:7px;font-family:arial,sans-serif;color:#000000;'>recurring costs. For 2012, refers to the 2012&#45;2014 Restructuring Program; for 2010 and 2011,
refers to reversals of 2004&#45;2008 Restructuring Program costs.</div> </td></tr></table></div>
